To solve this problem, we need to iterate through the array of cities, check each city to see if it meets the population criteria, and then find the city with the highest population. Here's a JavaScript code snippet to achieve that:

```javascript
const germanyCities = [
  { name: "Berlin", population: 3769000 },
  { name: "Hamburg", population: 1845000 },
  { name: "Munich", population: 1472000 },
  { name: "Cologne", population: 1088000 },
  { name: "Frankfurt", population: 753056 },
  { name: "Stuttgart", population: 634830 },
  { name: "Düsseldorf", population: 619294 },
  { name: "Dortmund", population: 588994 },
  { name: "Essen", population: 583109 },
  { name: "Leipzig", population: 570087 },
  { name: "Bremen", population: 568321 },
  { name: "Dresden", population: 555805 },
  { name: "Hanover", population: 532163 },
  { name: "Nuremberg", population: 518370 },
  { name: "Duisburg", population: 498590 },
  { name: "Bochum", population: 364628 },
  { name: "Wuppertal", population: 354382 },
  { name: "Bielefeld", population: 333786 },
  { name: "Bonn", population: 327913 },
  { name: "Münster", population: 315293 },
];

let largestCity = null;

// Loop through each city in the array
for (const city of germanyCities) {
  // Check if the city meets the population criteria
  if (city.population >= 100000) {
    // If no city has been set as largestCity or the current city has a larger population, update largestCity
    if (!largestCity || city.population > largestCity.population) {
      largestCity = city;
    }
  }
}

if (largestCity) {
  console.log(`The largest city in Germany with a population of at least 100,000 is ${largestCity.name} with a population of ${largestCity.population}.`);
} else {
  console.log("No city meets the criteria.");
}
```

Running this code will output:

```
The largest city in Germany with a population of at least 100,000 is Berlin with a population of 3769000.
```

This code iterates over each city, checks if the population is at least 100,000, and keeps track of the city with the largest population that meets this condition.
